PrecisAppointment of FERRY de KERCKHOVE as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of Indonesia; LOUISE LÉGER as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of Costa Rica; PHILIP MacKINNON as Ambassador of Canada to the Islamic Republic of Iran; ANDREW McALISTER as Ambassador of Canada to the Kingdom of Thailand, with concurrent accreditation to the Lao People's Democratic Republic and the Union of Myanmar; KONRAD SIGURDSON as High Commissioner for Canada in the Islamic Republic of Pakistan; HOWARD STRAUSS as High Commissioner for Canada in the Federal Republic of Nigeria; and DENIS THIBAULT as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of Senegal.
